{"tid":132184,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"好老實講 叻既年青人一定係考警察","createTime":"2017-02-23T15:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T15:56:23.000Z","uid":54581,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4243ce2b4c89e10bb74fe6db7962306da6a8ccc1","tid":132184,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:44:02.000Z","msg":"再叻啲一定要考PI<br />\n<br />\n人工高，福利好。<br />\n<br />\n聽高登啲傻仔講，而對份工有偏見既<br />\n<br />\n你智商高極有限。"},{"pid":"85f173a78561fd6f296388cfe4f729630a245b7f","tid":132184,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"好老實，起薪兩皮野<br />\n<br />\n等十年，30歲，當仲係散仔都近3皮野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n趁班傻仔仲係到抗拒考警既時候入隊<br />\n<br />\n到時就到你做人生贏家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然英文好既，一定要考PI"},{"pid":"f67db580b7565d31302b1ee66f13eef15d3006b6","tid":132184,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:48:12.000Z","msg":"當班憤青大學生仲為搵工而煩惱<br />\n<br />\n仲以為freshgrad 搵萬八就好勁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你諗下自己點揀。<br />\n<br />\n有學位既更加應該識諗"},{"pid":"9ecadad68adfd58908a788a169685f415245215a","tid":132184,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"真心，做警察好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好做驚犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}